they're bigger than
any flora I've seen.

12
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:21,208
In the night, they
utter strange sounds,

13
00:02:21,291 --> 00:02:22,750
but more bizarre is their taste

14
00:02:22,833 --> 00:02:25,375
for attacking guests
that visit the castle.

15
00:02:25,458 --> 00:02:27,416
It was because of this
that rumors about us

16
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:31,875
being vampires began to spread
before we knew it to be true.

17
00:02:31,958 --> 00:02:33,583
Young Arystar...

18
00:02:33,666 --> 00:02:36,041
Your destiny has
been chosen for you...

19
00:02:36,125 --> 00:02:39,625
In this castle you will live the
remainder of your lifetime...

20
00:02:39,708 --> 00:02:41,208
It is now your responsibility

21
00:02:41,291 --> 00:02:44,166
to tend to our
beautiful flower garden...

22
00:02:44,250 --> 00:02:47,833
