new Exorcist in fang boy...

261
00:18:40,125 --> 00:18:42,083
So it wasn't a
total waste of time.

262
00:18:42,166 --> 00:18:44,666
Yeah.

263
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:48,791
Come on Allen,
there's no need for you

264
00:18:48,875 --> 00:18:50,458
to act like you did
something wrong...

265
00:18:50,541 --> 00:18:54,166
I mean, granted, this may not be
the ideal outcome for Krory...

266
00:18:54,250 --> 00:18:55,750
But the fact is he
needed a reason

267
00:18:55,833 --> 00:18:58,333
to go on living and
you gave that to him...

268
00:18:58,416 --> 00:19:00,458
Given some time,
he'll feel better.

269
00:19:00,541 --> 00:19:02,250
I promise...

270
00:19:02,333 --> 00:19:04,333
That was an elegant speech...

271
00:19:04,416 --> 00:19:05,375
Way to scare me!

272
00:19:05,458 --> 00:19:06,541
Old fart...!

273
00:19:06,625 --> 00:19:08,166
How long have you
been standing there?!

274
00:19:08,250 --> 00:19:09,541
I just got here.

275
00:19:09,625 --> 00:19:11,333
You really worry
about me that much...?

276
00:19:11,416 --> 00:19:12,958
I can take care of myself.

277
00:19:13,041 --> 00:19:14,458
I solved this case
with less effort

278
00:19:14,541 --> 00:19:16,791
than it takes to change
one of your diapers.

279
00:19:19,958 --> 00:19:21,791
That really hurt you geezer!

280
00:19:21,875 --> 00:19:24,416
Don't talk to me about
effort you slimy punk!

281
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:25,791
You could've used
some of that "effort"

282
00:19:25,875 --> 00:19:27,583
to avoid damaging the castle!

283
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:30,208
Well excuse me but I was
trying not to get myself killed.

284
00:19:30,291 --> 00:19:32,375
Try listening first
before you hit me panda!

285
00:19:32,458 --> 00:19:34,000
I didn't hit you, I kicked you!

286
00:19:34,083 --> 00:19:35,125
Don't you know the difference?

287
00:19:35,208 --> 00:19:36,375
It's the same thing!

288
00:19:36,458 --> 00:19:37,666
No it is not!

289
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:39,083
What have you been
doing this whole time,

290
00:19:39,166 --> 00:19:41,083
lounging around
and eatin' prunes?

291
00:19:48,625 --> 00:19:49,875
Don't tell me...

292
00:19:56,541 --> 00:19:59,958
Wait... He's still
in there... Krory!!!

293
00:20:15,541 --> 00:20:16,875
Look at your faces...

294
00:20:16,958 --> 00:20:18,791
You thought I died...

295
00:20:18,875 --> 00:20:21,458
I'm sorry if I gave
you all a scare.

296
00:20:21,541 --> 00:20:24,791
But as you can see, I'm fine.

297
00:20:24,875 --> 00:20:26,375
You should know...

298
00:20:26,458 --> 00:20:29,583
I fully intend on devoting my
life to becoming an Exorcist.

299
00:20:31,375 --> 00:20:33,875
Great!

300
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,916
Eliade...

301
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:41,208
I have made destroying
Akuma my new life's work...

302
00:20:41,291 --> 00:20:44,791
Otherwise... what right
did I have to destroy you...?

303
00:20:46,208 --> 00:20:49,458
I hope you understand, my love.

304
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,166
Our new friend and colleague,

305
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:42,291
Krory, joins us on a mission...

306
00:22:42,375 --> 00:22:44,791
But his inexperience
outside of his castle shows

307
00:22:44,875 --> 00:22:47,250
when his actions
put us in danger...

308
00:22:47,333 --> 00:22:52,208
Next time on D. Gray-man:
"Krory's New Beginning."

309
00:22:52,291 --> 00:22:55,791
Bring forth salvation to
this tormented Akuma's soul.

